name: Flex 3 Beta
shortDescription: Develop your own tweaks and share them on the Flex Community Cloud

users.issues: App and cloud patches work, but creating your own patches currently does not. Processing executables does not work at the moment.
Newest update gives full iOS 11 support
Shows processing error on iPad Air 2

There exist issues, at unknown times or reasons, whereupon some apps which have one or more patches ACTIVATED (e.g. switched on) will crash upon launch (immediately and sometimes taking down Springboard with it).  However I believe a new version is available that may fix this issue, I will report back once I’ve updated.
